race.description: Memberships Open Now Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: TOKE (5) sets up well third-up with added fitness and should race handy. He'll be poised to strike when they quicken. VELKA (6) has been around the mark in both runs back, is fitter now, and draws to advantage. Capable of giving this a real shake. MARKWELL MELODY (7) finds an easier assignment and should be peaking with three runs under her belt. A minor-hope with upside. MORPETH (4) struggled on debut, but the booking of Bullock is noteworthy. Sharp improvement wouldn't shock.
